    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera S is a true time capsule, presented in a condition that is indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom. The Basalt Black Metallic paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes, protected by a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the Carrera Red natural leather remains supple and fragrant, with no creasing on the bolsters and zero wear on the touchpoints. Every electronic system, from the adaptive suspension to the premium sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, accompanied by a fastidious service history and a spotless engine bay that shows no signs of age or leakage. For the collector who accepts nothing less than perfection, this investment-grade 911 offers the rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its peak form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
